data.description: Great 4 Bed 2.5 Bath home nestled in Sun Meadows neighborhood in Jenks School District! Beautiful kitchen with a white stone wall surrounding the double oven, cooktop range, and extra cabinet space! Enjoy the views of in-ground pool and backyard from the sunroom that offers lots of natural light. Living room with stone fireplace and white built-in bookcases. Downstairs Master suite with walk-in shower, bathtub, and walk-in closet. Formal dining. Game/rec room, flex room and three bedrooms upstairs all with walk-in closets. So many great features - Make this one yours!
